{
  "stem": "449.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They notified my wife to pick up the kid, but she couldn't enter the room.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My oldest son was with me, and the police came and took him from me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he clings to me and wrestles with the police.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Today he says that was when he started to hate police.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They broke his hand and took him off of me and took him out to the mother, so I was arrested and put in a big bus.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they were all Jews, and there were many Jews, Hassidims, you know, with the payots and a long caftan.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And on the French camion, the French bus, there were two soldiers in front, and one with the French flag, and would whistle, and they are taking us through Marseilles.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The first German prisoners.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The Jews with the payots, the first German prisoners.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We couldn't explain, we are not Germans, we are Jews.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We are better enemies of Hitler then you have.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You are going to prison.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was two years in a real prison, and from there, they took me in the camp.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But before I talk about that, I would like to talk about the care HIAS took of us.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They paid for the hotel.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Still, as I said, I got some money from my friend, but it was not enough.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "A certain amount from Switzerland from the mother of the architect, so that was how we survived with this little money.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Also, I could take a job from a businessman who had stores.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They wanted advertising on the big glass windows, so I made the lettering, whatever they wanted to say, and I cut it out and different colors that they wanted.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And at night, I went out and glued it on the windows.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
